<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Hi <%= @submission.name %>,
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you for registering for the PHAS Symposium 2017. We have recorded the following information.
    </p>
    <% if @submission.presentation_type != "attender" %>
      <p>
        Title:
        <br/>
        <%= @submission.title %>
      </p>
      <p>
        Abstract:
        <br/>
        <%= @submission.abstract %>
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <p>
        You will be attending, but not presenting.
      </p>
    <% end%>

    <% if @submission.attender_type != "undergrad" %>
      <p>
        Please submit the $5 registration fee to one of the following people:
       <ul>
         <li>Abdullah Khalid (SB306)</li>
         <li>Anna Ordog (SB 628C)</li>
         <li>Elizabeth Watt (TBCC CCB17)</li>
         <li>Mehrnoosh Tahani (SB 512)</li>
       <ul>
      </p>
    <% else %>
      <p>
        You are an undergraduate. Your registration is free.
      </p>
    <% end %>

    <p>
      A detailed schedule will be provided closer to the date of the symposium.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns please contact <%= link_to 'Anna (aordog@ucalgary.ca)', 'mailto:f.mivehvar@ucalgary.ca' %>, or <%= link_to 'Elizabeth (erwatt@ucalgary.ca)', 'mailto:erwatt@ucalgary.ca' %>
    </p>

    <p>
      Thank you.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
